## App 2: Payload CMS (emwraps-cms)

### Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 16.1.6 + Payload CMS v3.78
- **Node.js**: v22 LTS (REQUIRED вАФ v20 has ESM issues, v24 has breaking changes)
- **Database**: `@payloadcms/db-postgres` вЖТ Supabase Postgres (session pooler, `cms` schema)
- **Storage**: `@payloadcms/storage-s3` вЖТ Supabase Storage S3 вЬЕ Verified working
- **Rich Text**: `@payloadcms/richtext-lexical`
- **Auth**: Payload's built-in auth (CMS admins only)
- **CORS**: Handled natively by Payload's `cors` config array (NOT Next.js custom headers)
- **Deployment**: Coolify вЖТ `cms.emwraps.net`

