## App 3: EMWRAPS Tickets (emwraps-tickets)

### Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Vite + React 19
- **Styling**: Vanilla CSS (dark sci-fi HUD design system вАФ matches emwraps-react)
- **Routing**: React Router v7 (`react-router-dom`)
- **State Management**: Zustand
- **Database**: Supabase (client SDK вАФ same project as frontend & CMS)
- **Auth**: Supabase Auth (email/password, role-based RBAC)
- **Deployment**: Coolify вЖТ `tickets.emwraps.net`

### Pages

| Page | Route | Description |
|------|-------|-------------|
| Dashboard | `/` | Stats overview, today's tickets, activity feed |
| Ticket List | `/tickets` | Filterable list with card/table/calendar views |
| Ticket Create | `/tickets/new` | Multi-step ticket creation form |
| Ticket Detail | `/tickets/:id` | Full ticket view with services, materials, workers |
| Customer List | `/customers` | Searchable customer directory |
| Customer Detail | `/customers/:id` | Profile with vehicles & ticket history |
| Inventory | `/inventory` | Products, serial numbers, stock levels |
| Workers | `/workers` | Team overview with status & assignments |
| Schedule | `/schedule` | Calendar view for scheduling |
| Settings | `/settings` | App settings, user management |
| Login | `/login` | Email/password auth |

### Auth Model
- **Roles**: `admin`, `manager`, `worker`, `staff`
- **Admin**: Full access to all features
- **Manager**: All except user management
- **Worker**: View assigned tickets, update status
- **Staff**: View-only access to tickets

### Key Design Decisions
- **UI/UX matches emwraps-react**: Same dark sci-fi HUD design system (amber/gold accent, Outfit font, glassmorphism)
- **Sidebar layout**: Collapsible sidebar for admin navigation (not top navbar)
- **Service data**: CMS first вЖТ Supabase `service_structure` fallback вЖТ hardcoded fallback
- **CMS integration**: `src/lib/cms.js` fetches services from Payload CMS REST API
- **Same Supabase backend**: Shared auth/tables/RLS with frontend
- **Component size rule**: No single file exceeds 300 lines

### Key Files
- `src/lib/supabase.js` вАФ Supabase client (shared project)
- `src/lib/cms.js` вАФ CMS API client (services from Payload)
- `src/stores/ticketStore.js` вАФ Ticket CRUD with customer/vehicle find-or-create
- `src/stores/serviceStore.js` вАФ Service tree (CMS вЖТ Supabase вЖТ fallback cascade)
- `src/stores/workerStore.js` вАФ Worker profiles from `profiles` table
- `src/stores/inventoryStore.js` вАФ Serial numbers / products CRUD
- `src/hooks/useAuth.js` вАФ Auth session + profile with permissions
- `supabase/migrations/001_create_all_tables.sql` вАФ Full DB schema + seed

